&lt;p&gt;Core Midwife Maternity Level 4&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you an experienced Band 6 midwife passionate about providing excellent antenatal and postnatal care?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a Core Band 6 midwife to join the Maternity Level 4 Team. Across the floor we run the antenatal, induction of labour, transitional care, early discharge lounge and postnatal care services&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The applicant with be responsible for the day to day running of the ward areas; leading the team, promoting safety and excellence by being the clinical expert on shift, coordinating care and liaising with the multidisciplinary team. This will require excellent leadership, managerial and communication skills. This popular opportunity enables midwives to maintain expertise in both low and high risk care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact Milica Redfearn milica.redfearn@royalberkshire.nhs.uk or 01183228936&lt;/p&gt;
